      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples representative of production device; sample size and variability documented.",
      "rationale": "FDA experimental dataset used three pump units from the same manufacturing batch. Sample-to-sample variability in RHI < 6% reported by FDA. Representative of production geometry within dimensional tolerances."
    },
