      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation input parameters match experimental conditions within stated uncertainty bounds.",
      "rationale": "All simulation boundary conditions set to match experimental nominal values. Flow rate, rotational speed, and fluid temperature matched to within experimental uncertainty. Inlet turbulence intensity set to 5% based on upstream tubing characterization — consistent with experimental setup."
